  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies whether white space should be ignored in the base 64 transformation.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[

## Remarks
 White space includes the space character as well as tab characters, newline characters, and so on. Characters that constitute white space are those identified by the <xref:System.Char.IsWhiteSpace*?displayProperty=nameWithType> method.

 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
